Introduction
============

About
-----
PhenoImageShare (PhIS) is a cross-species, cross-repository tool enabling semantic discovery, 
browsing and annotation of phenotypical images.PhIS is a collaborative open source project 
between EMBL-EBI, MRC Human Genetics Unit at The University of Edinburgh and Heriot-Watt University.

The frontend web application is developed with Python, Django and Javascript. 
The backend services are developed primarily with Java and exposed via RESTful APIs. 


Getting started
---------------
PhenoImageShare web application can be accessed at http://beta.phenoimageshare.org. 


Backend Services & APIs
-----------------------
Data Access APIs can be accessed at http://beta.phenoimageshare.org/data.
Middleware APIs can be accessed at http://beta.phenoimageshare.org/middleware/IQS.


License & Releases
------------------
PhIS is released under Apache Version 2.0. Please see at http://beta.phenoimageshare.org/release/license
The following sections provide the change logs for the PhIS GUI beta releases. 
Please see data release notes at http://beta.phenoimageshare.org/release/data


============ Beta Release 1.3 =============

Release status
--------------
3 July 2015 beta release

Details of Change
-----------------

New features
	1. None
	

Bug fixes
	1. Fixed broken line in "search" field/button on the search page by changing background of button - PHIS-202
	2. 


Other changes
	1. Renamed facet for "Taxon" to "Species" - PHIS-238
	2. On results page, "record" replaced with "image" - PHIS-237
	3. Added clickable example of queries under the search box - PHIS-239
	4. Simplifed headers for results table - PHIS-236
	5. Removed "proc."/ procedure from detail view - PHIS-230
	6. Renamed "Hots" to "Repository" - PHIS-227
	7. Landing page: displayed short summary of PhIS - PHIS-223
	8. Removed "image type" metadata display from detail view - PHIS-216
	9. Fixed anatomy annotations missing from results table - 214
	10. Changed color for search box & button to green / teal - PHIS-151
	11. Added more genotype information in results table - PHIS-234
	12. Search box - pressing enter or autosuggest select now triggers search - PHIS-233
	13. Removed display of empty channels on detail view - PHIS-232
	14. Changed style of metadata values on detail view - PHIS-220
	15. Search page: added explicit clear button - PHIS-211
	16. Added the number of images to pie chart tooltips - PHIS-244
	17. Added staining information as "Visualization" - PHIS-225

Known issues  
	1. Facets: Search text disappears from a facet search box when another facet search box is activated (clicked)
	2. GUI should send email to list when database connectivity issue - PHIS-111
	3. Adding copyright information for dataset / images 
	4. Number of records displayed on table does not correspond to selection - Search page - PHIS-106
	5. RESTful implementation, allowing users to go back to search URL history.
	6. Add whitespace between phenotype annotations on search page - PHIS-185
	
	
	
